      • getSerializedSize

        public int getSerializedSize()
        从类复制的说明: WritableRequest
        Get the size of the request in serialized form. The number returned by this function can't be less than the actual size - if the size can't be calculated correctly return WritableRequest.UNKNOWN_SIZE.
        覆盖:
        getSerializedSize 在类中 WritableRequest
        返回:
        The size (in bytes) of serialized request, or WritableRequest.UNKNOWN_SIZE if the size is not known or too expensive to calculate.
